üåê API Gateway Documentation: /studying_project
These endpoints process data and forward it to your external AI service (AI_BASE_URL_new_one). All requests are POST with a JSON body.

General Request Structure
Request Type	Purpose	Request Body Structure
Single Request	Process one item.	{ "key_a": "value", "key_b": "value" }
Batch Request	Process multiple items at once.	{ "requests": [{ "id": 1, "key_a": "value" }, ...] }

Export to Sheets
1. Get Script API
Endpoint: /studying_project/getting_script_from_video
AI Target: /getting_script

Single Request
Field	Example Value	Description	Required
input_link	"https://youtu.be/abc"	The URL of the video.	Yes
language	"en"	Language code for the script.	Yes

Export to Sheets
Status	Example Response Body
200 OK	{"script_content": "The full, segmented video transcript..."}
400/500 Error	{"error": "Script API failed", "details": "External error details"}

Export to Sheets
Batch Request
Field	Example Value	Description
requests	[{"id": 1, "input_link": "link1", "language": "en"}, ...]	List of items to process, each must have a unique id.

Export to Sheets
Status	Example Response Body
200 OK	{"results": [{"id": 1, "response": {"script_content": "..."}}, {"id": 2, "error": "language is required"}]}

Export to Sheets
2. Summarize API
Endpoint: /studying_project/summarize
AI Target: /summarize

Single Request
Field	Example Value	Description	Required
input_text	"The long text to be condensed."	The content for summarization.	Yes

Export to Sheets
Status	Example Response Body
200 OK	{"summary": "A concise summary of the input."}
400/500 Error	{"error": "Summarize API failed", "details": "External error details"}

Export to Sheets
3. Chat API
Endpoint: /studying_project/chat
AI Target: /chat

Single Request
Field	Example Value	Description	Required
input_text	"Context text for Q&A."	The context/document the AI should answer from.	Yes
question	"What is the main topic?"	The specific question to ask the AI.	Yes

Export to Sheets
Status	Example Response Body
200 OK	{"answer": "The AI's response based on the context."}
400/500 Error	{"error": "Chat API failed", "details": "External error details"}

Export to Sheets
4. Extract Main Points API
Endpoint: /studying_project/extract_main_points
AI Target: /extract_main_points

Single Request
Field	Example Value	Description	Required
input_text	"Detailed text with key arguments."	The content for point extraction.	Yes

Export to Sheets
Status	Example Response Body
200 OK	{"main_points": ["Point 1: ...", "Point 2: ..."]}
400/500 Error	{"error": "Extract API failed", "details": "External error details"}
